 I wish it were as simple as you think. That those who serve Gods of good are always good. I have seen too many so- called &quot;Druid&quot; attacking their wolf and bear allies...&quot;Just because.&quot; Paladins who are self-rightous and smug as they kill a creature who is friendly to them. Simply for greed. Evil is in what you do, not in what you are born or trained as. <br>
 I do NOT choose to &quot;sit on a fence&quot; and stand aside as evil runs amok. I oppose any and all who cause and delight in misery and suffering. I choose to fight evil. No matter whom or what the evil is. I wish my skills were more equal to yours, then I would challenge you. In time, Shintou. If your maddness has not destroyed you by the time I am more powerful...I will kill you. I do not fear death.<br>
<br>
