<br>
One should not expect the lightbringers to understand Innoruuk or His message.  They are deluded fools, hypocrites because even within their &quot;pure&quot; hearts they harbor hatred of what they label &quot;evil.&quot;  The are willfully ignorant and seek to stomp out the truth, and the truth is that it is only through conflict that growth occurs, that without conflict all is static and truly dead.  They ignore the great motivator of conflict: Hate...pure, perfect Hate.<br>
