They refuse to accept the truth of Lord Innoruuk's message, and seek to exterminate those of us who He purified to be the perfect vessals of His message.  Our mission is to see that Hate is propgated, and spread.  It is a Holy Sacrament to cause the flawed vessals created by Tunare to Hate us, made more enjoyable by their insane denial of it, or their rationalizations of it.  The worst offenders are the worshippers of nature, who refuse to accept the place of hate and death out of bigoted foolishness, and the utter hypocrisy of the paladins who hate us for our &quot;evil ways.&quot;<br>
<br>
